description:
TRY OUR JETPACK CITY MAZES : THE GRAVITY CLASH OF 2 WORLDS GAME

City becomes really strange. You are controlling the jet pack character in the air by you have to avoid all obstacles on your way and try to fly between the buildings of 2 worlds.

You will notice lots of changes in the city but try to save the kids who are on top. If you save enough kids than you will get a chance to unlock 4 new powerful jet packs.

How to play?

- Tap on jetpack to fly in the air
- Fly between buildings on your way
- Save kids as much as possible to unlock new powerful jetpacks characters
